OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMist and low cloud soon burning
OL,6,Foff this morning. Otherwise all parts
OL,7,Fwill have a dry day with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Feeling quite warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,12,Flate sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be dry with mostly clear
OL,14,Fskies but some fog and low cloud
OL,15,Fpossible later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAny overnight fog and low
OL,18,Fcloud burning off through the morning
OL,19,Fto leave a dry, very warm and sunny
OL,20,Fday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
