OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday, chance
OL,7,Fof a few showers. Cooler and and
OL,8,Fcloudier over the weekend with a
OL,9,Fchance of showers.
